      "span_text": "After introduction of the 15 nt deletion into the NS reverse-genetics plasmid using the QuikChange II kit (Stratagene), the two recombinant IAVs (WT-MZ and NSdel8084-MZ), both derived from the MZ virus described above, were rescued by reverse genetics as described previously  ."
